# Paws Plaza Feature

## Overview
The Paws Plaza is the main social feed where users discover pet content from the community. It features a waterfall/masonry grid layout with filtering capabilities.

## Screen Structure

### PlazaScreen (Main)
- **Location**: `lib/features/plaza/plaza_screen.dart`
- **Components**:
  - App bar with title "Paws Plaza" and search icon
  - Horizontal scrolling filter chips (All, #Dogs, #Cats, #NewbieGuide, #CutePics, #Training)
  - Masonry grid of post cards (2 columns)
  - Pull-to-refresh functionality

### ProfileScreen (Sub-page)
- **Location**: `lib/features/plaza/profile_screen.dart`
- **Components**:
  - Back button
  - User avatar (large, circular)
  - Username and display name
  - Bio and quote
  - Follow button (softCoral)
  - Grid of user's posts (3 columns)

