## Data Flow

### Mock Data
- Generate 20-30 sample posts in `mock_data_service.dart`
- Use Unsplash URLs for images:
  - Dogs: `https://images.unsplash.com/photo-[id]?w=400`
  - Cats: Similar pattern
- Sample usernames: @DogLover_Mark, @CatMom_Sarah, @StylishPaws

### Filtering Logic
```dart
List<Post> filterPosts(List<Post> posts, String filter) {
  if (filter == 'All') return posts;
  return posts.where((post) => post.tags.contains(filter)).toList();
}
```

### State Management
```dart
class _PlazaScreenState extends State<PlazaScreen> {
  List<Post> _allPosts = [];
  List<Post> _filteredPosts = [];
  String _selectedFilter = 'All';
  bool _isLoading = true;

  @override
  void initState() {
    super.initState();
    _loadPosts();
  }

  void _loadPosts() async {
    // Load from MockDataService
    setState(() {
      _allPosts = MockDataService.getPosts();
      _filteredPosts = _allPosts;
      _isLoading = false;
    });
  }

  void _onFilterChanged(String filter) {
    setState(() {
      _selectedFilter = filter;
      _filteredPosts = filterPosts(_allPosts, filter);
    });
  }
}
```

