## UI Specifications

### Post Card
- Border radius: 16px
- Shadow: soft, subtle
- Image: AspectRatio varies (natural image size)
- Content padding: 12px
- Caption: 14px, medium weight, 1-2 lines max (ellipsis)
- Author row: 12px text, 20px avatar, 8px spacing

### Filter Chips
- Height: 32px
- Padding: 12px horizontal
- Border radius: 16px (full pill)
- Font: 14px, semibold
- Active: softCoral bg, white text
- Inactive: panelWhite/darkGray bg, default text

### Profile Screen
- Avatar: 96px diameter
- Name: 24px, bold
- Bio: 14px, mediumGray
- Quote: 14px, italic
- Follow button: 48px height, full rounded, softCoral
- Post grid: 3 columns, 4px gap, square aspect ratio

